name: Fairy Ruby & Little Pimp
description:
Fairy Ruby, a free spirit who walked on the wild side and was trapped in an illusory world.

Little Pimp, short but nervous, swallows drinks with strange names and smokes cigarettes of unknown brands. Likes to imprison free spirits.

*By collecting this piece owners will receive for free in their wallet my next NFT mint, the handmade watercolor version of Fairy Ruby & Little Pimp.
